#. </h1></div><blockquote class="gatha"><p><a class="sc" id="1"></a><a
#. class="verse-num-sc" id="verse-num-sc228"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
#. id="verse-num-pts228"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.4:5.1"
msgid "“Sukhañce jīvituṃ icche,"
msgstr "One who hopes for the ascetic life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:5.2"
msgid "sāmaññasmiṃ apekkhavā;"
msgstr "Wishing to live in happiness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:5.3"
msgid "Saṃghikaṃ nātimaññeyya,"
msgstr "Should not look down on the Saṅgha’s robe,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:5.4"
msgid "cīvaraṃ pānabhojanaṃ."
msgstr "Or its food and drinks."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="2"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc229"></a><a class="verse-num-pts" id="verse-num-pts229"></a>
msgctxt "thag3.4:6.1"
msgid "Sukhañce jīvituṃ icche,"
msgstr "One who hopes for the ascetic life,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:6.2"
msgid "sāmaññasmiṃ apekkhavā;"
msgstr "Wishing to live in happiness,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:6.3"
msgid "Ahi mūsikasobbhaṃva,"
msgstr "Should stay in the Saṅgha’s lodgings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "thag3.4:6.4"
msgid "sevetha sayanāsanaṃ."
msgstr "Like a snake in a mouse hole."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="3"></a><a class="verse-num-sc"
#. id="verse-num-sc230"></a><a class="verse-num-pts"
